│ transformation: creates inverted condition and swaps operands\n3. Final     │
│ result loses the nnan nsz flags entirely\n\nThe key issue is in the code at │
│ lines 4091-4092 where `CreateFCmpFMF` correctly preserves FMF from the      │
│ condition, but `CreateSelect` at line 4094 does not preserve the original   │
│ select's FMF.\n\n3. Root Cause Analysis:\n\nIn `InstCombineSelect.cpp`      │
│ around line 4091-4094, when canonicalizing min/max patterns, the code       │
