│ condition's FMF, but then creates a new select with plain `CreateSelect`    │
│ instead of `CreateSelectFMF` with the original select's fast-math           │
│ flags.\n\nThe original select instruction `SI` has nnan and nsz flags that  │
│ must be preserved in the transformed select, but the current code only uses │
│ `Builder.CreateSelect(Cmp, LHS, RHS, SI.getName(), &SI)` which doesn't      │
│ transfer the FMF.\n\n4. Proposed Edit Point(s):\n\nThe fix is to replace    │
│ the plain `CreateSelect` call with `CreateSelectFMF` that preserves the     │
│ original select's fast-math flags. Specifically, line 4094 should use       │
