│ preserving the fast-math flags from the original select instruction when    │
│ creating the new select, the transformation will maintain the same semantic │
│ guarantees (nnan ensures no NaN outputs, nsz treats signed zeros as         │
│ equivalent). This will make the transformation correct for all inputs       │
│ including SNaN values."})                                                   │
